#

Pan-Seared New York Steak with Mushroom Madeira Sauce

$35
650 kcal

Allergens:

MushroomsDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SteakGourmetSavoryRich

Description

A rich and savory New York steak, perfectly seared and paired with a luscious mushroom Madeira sauce that elevates the dish to gourmet status.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 16 oz
  • Mushrooms (cremini or button): 8 oz
  • Shallots: 1, minced
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Madeira wine: 1/2 cup
  • Beef broth: 1 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
